Her father Gavin Gill said: 'I’m confident that the legal system will handle it correctly, and the people that understand the facts of what’s going on and the character of all four of the youngsters that are involved in this will see this and handle it appropriately.'

Gill remains optimistic that the situation will be positive in the end.

'I do believe this whole thing is a way to help us grow and to learn from our mistakes and to move forward and just kind of get on with our lives.'

